metadata.name: Doodled Pizzas
metadata.description: Doodled Pizzas is a collection of 10,000 generative pizzas baked in 'The Oven'. 'The Chef' utilises 'The Oven' to bake and burn pizzas to ensure all pizzas are of the highest quality. 'The Chef' will also implement buybacks through 'The Cashier' to keep our pizzas hot-off-the-oven!
